# Users can create recipes
# Recipes have ingredients
Users have inventories
Making(cooking) a recipe adjusts Inventory
Users can CRUD recipes and inventories

# 1. Create Users, Recipes, Ingredients, Amounts(join table), Inventory
# 2. Users can Sign up
# 3. Users can login and logout
# 4. Users can create a recipe
5. Users can take Inventory
6. Users can search a recipe by ingredient.
7. Validations to ensure user can only view or edit their own content.
# 8. Secure passwords
9. OmniAuth login
